the mother too has come.

1164
02:12:45,222 --> 02:12:48,316
- You too come along. Come
- Jaggu.

1165
02:12:51,228 --> 02:12:54,664
Brother, Gandhiji said
to return the bottles.

1166
02:12:55,833 --> 02:12:58,802
Hey John, thank you
very much. I' m getting married.

1167
02:13:02,739 --> 02:13:05,799
- You must come. Don't forget.
- But who's the girl?

1168
02:13:06,243 --> 02:13:09,940
It must be a special
girl who put down my meter.

1169
02:13:10,247 --> 02:13:12,681
Friend, but tell us who it is.

