02:13:12,850 --> 02:13:15,614
She's a true lndian woman.

1171
02:13:15,853 --> 02:13:21,621
Like Savitri, Sakubai,
Anusuya, Meerabai.

1172
02:13:21,758 --> 02:13:24,022
She's always praying,
all the time.

1173
