I can't understand
when you pray & when you drink!

1176
02:13:46,283 --> 02:13:50,242
- l' m feeling dizzy
- Stupid ass!

1177
02:13:50,554 --> 02:13:53,045
I asked for a bottle and
you vanished.

1178
02:13:53,957 --> 02:13:55,424
Bottle, again?

1179
02:13:55,692 --> 02:13:57,250
Forgot what Gandhiji said?

1180
02:13:57,461 --> 02:14:01,591
Look if you want to drink, get
your own bottle.Don't bother me!

1181
02:14:02,299 --> 02:14:05,063
Next week we' re getting married
so don't talk like this!

1182
02:14:06,303 --> 02:14:07,395
Marriage?

1183
02:14:09,306 --> 02:14:11,934
- Whose marriage?
- Mine

1184
02:14:12,976 --> 02:14:15,274
How funny!
You' re getting married?

1185
02:14:18,882 --> 02:14:19,940
To whom?

1186
02:14:22,319 --> 02:14:23,479
You, who else!

1187
02:14:23,921 --> 02:14:28,085
- Me? - Yes.
- Drunk without drink?

1188
02:14:28,725 --> 02:14:33,059
Look, I've tolerated enough
if I get angry... then?

1189
02:14:33,630 --> 02:14:35,962
Go, go whom are you threatening?

1190
02:14:36,033 --> 02:14:39,298
Why should I marry you?

1191
02:14:40,337 --> 02:14:44,706
Don't make me angry or l' ll
give you one slap on your face!

1192
02:14:47,344 --> 02:14:50,905
You son of a taxi lay
a finger on me and see!

1193
02:14:51,348 --> 02:14:54,909
- You want to see?
- Yes, I want to!

1194
02:14:58,355 --> 02:15:02,587
- Want to see more?
- Yes!

1195
02:15:03,026 --> 02:15:06,484
I have no one who' ll
save me. Beat me more.

1196
02:15:08,699 --> 02:15:11,133
Now if you raise your hand,
l' ll rip it out.

1197
02:15:12,369 --> 02:15:16,373
I also know one shouldn't
hit women but when the taxi..

1198
02:15:16,373 --> 02:15:20,139
..doesn't start it has to be
pushed. We marry next week.

1199
02:15:20,377 --> 02:15:22,345
... and now she's pretending.
- Again?

1200
02:15:22,546 --> 02:15:25,515
- When did I agree to marry you?
- l' ll show you!

1201
02:15:26,383 --> 02:15:31,013
See! See! You won't marry me?

1202
02:15:31,388 --> 02:15:33,356
Am I mad?

1203
02:15:33,790 --> 02:15:36,850
Bitch! In front of God
you accepted and now you deny!

1204
02:15:36,994 --> 02:15:40,361
She can never
belong to one man.

1205
02:15:40,664 --> 02:15:46,003
- What do you mean?
- You pretend to love me and...

1206
02:15:46,003 --> 02:15:49,530
Pretend to marry him.
- What? Pretending to love you?

1207
02:15:49,740 --> 02:15:52,174
- All false!
- Then what's true, this?

1208
02:15:52,409 --> 02:15:59,781
No, Manju has always loved
you and will only love you!

1209
02:16:00,417 --> 02:16:04,376
- Who is Manju? - She, who else?
what name did she give you?

1210
02:16:04,621 --> 02:16:06,646
Savitri, Anusuya, Sita.

1211
02:16:08,425 --> 02:16:09,983
But she is Anju!

1212
02:16:13,430 --> 02:16:16,991
Jaggu, that Balma,
Auntie, kidnap, Manju.

1213
02:16:17,100 --> 02:16:19,193
What nonsense is that?
Speak clearly.

1214
02:16:19,836 --> 02:16:23,067
Some Balma has
kidnapped Auntie and Manju.

1215
02:16:23,440 --> 02:16:27,069
- But l' m right here.
- But you are Anju!

1216
02:16:27,444 --> 02:16:30,038
- I am Manju!
- One minute, one minute!

1217
02:16:30,113 --> 02:16:35,141
He was saying two kittens,
twins Anju-Manju...

1218
02:16:35,452 --> 02:16:39,411
- Twins?
- Twin sister?

1219
02:16:40,457 --> 02:16:46,828
Take care of this menace.
She's the root of our problems.

1220
02:16:47,464 --> 02:16:50,433
Finish her off! Once she's no
more, we' ll have no problems!

1221
02:16:50,734 --> 02:16:54,431
Uncle, let me go.
I've done nothing!

1222
02:16:54,738 --> 02:16:57,707
You haven't so far,
but now you will.

1223
02:16:58,475 --> 02:17:00,443
Today is your 21 st birthday...

1224
02:17:00,877 --> 02:17:04,881
... and according to
your father's will,...

1225
02:17:04,881 --> 02:17:07,441
... you inherit everything
today.

1226
02:17:08,485 --> 02:17:11,488
- What's written in it? - That
of your own sweet will,...

1227
02:17:11,488 --> 02:17:13,490
... without any compulsions,...

1228
02:17:13,490 --> 02:17:16,857
... you' re willing
the property over to me.

1229
02:17:17,094 --> 02:17:20,689
- You are, aren't you?
- No child, no!

1230
02:17:20,831 --> 02:17:24,130
- Don't sign or they' ll kill
you! - Quiet, old woman!

1231
02:17:25,502 --> 02:17:27,970
- Sign it, dear Anju!
- l' ll sign.

1232
02:17:30,507 --> 02:17:34,068
- Sign!
- Where? - Here.

1233
02:17:40,517 --> 02:17:42,883
Stop Jaggu! He's got
a revolver in his hand.

1234
02:17:43,520 --> 02:17:45,488
- Then what do we do? - We' ll
think of some plan. Come.

1235
02:17:50,794 --> 02:17:52,785
Do you know
what's written in this?

1236
02:17:53,530 --> 02:17:57,762
That l' m committing suicide!

1237
02:17:58,535 --> 02:18:00,503
Wait Mr. Tribhuvandas, wait!

1238
02:18:04,941 --> 02:18:07,000
This signature is false,
so is the girl!

1239
02:18:08,545 --> 02:18:12,003
She's not Anju but Manju,
this taxi driver's Manju.

1240
02:18:12,549 --> 02:18:16,086
- Taxi driver's Manju?
- Yes, according to his plan...

1241
02:18:16,086 --> 02:18:17,917
Manju came and started
living in your house.

1242
02:18:19,556 --> 02:18:22,116
And he kidnapped my poor Anju.

1243
02:18:22,559 --> 02:18:26,325
- What nonsense are you talking?
- You' ll know soon. Talk!

1244
02:18:26,563 --> 02:18:31,523
- No.
- Will you talk or not?

1245
02:18:32,969 --> 02:18:34,334
You' re strange!

1246
02:18:34,571 --> 02:18:36,835
Put me in this situation
and watch the fun coolly!

1247
02:18:36,907 --> 02:18:38,807
Tell them
what's our relationship.

1248
02:18:39,576 --> 02:18:45,708
- Your relation with Anju?
- Not her, but her, my Laila...

1249
02:18:46,183 --> 02:18:50,347
... Amba.
- What? Are you bonkers?

1250
02:18:50,587 --> 02:18:53,351
Yes, that's why, in greed,
I listened to you.

1251
02:18:54,591 --> 02:18:57,958
Here, stay here yes,
tell me what did she say?

1252
02:18:58,595 --> 02:18:59,960
I' ll tell you all.

1253
02:19:00,096 --> 02:19:02,866
She saw me once
with Manju and came to me...

1254
02:19:02,866 --> 02:19:05,101
... and said send Manju
to my house...

1255
02:19:05,101 --> 02:19:09,197
... and they'd have murdered you.

1256
02:19:09,272 --> 02:19:11,570
And we' ll he 50-50
partners in the inheritance.

1257
02:19:11,641 --> 02:19:14,303
- Shall I go?
- He's lying!

1258
02:19:14,411 --> 02:19:16,743
- I never saw him before!
- Shameless!

1259
02:19:17,280 --> 02:19:20,841
I' ll sort her out later.
First lets check out Anju-Manju.

1260
02:19:21,017 --> 02:19:24,851
- Tell us, who is she?
- She, she...

1261
02:19:25,021 --> 02:19:27,182
She's my daughter, Manju.

1262
02:19:28,625 --> 02:19:29,853
I' m Anju!

1263
02:19:32,629 --> 02:19:35,598
If she's Manju!
Where's Anju?

1264
02:19:36,633 --> 02:19:37,861
I know where she is!

1265
02:19:38,034 --> 02:19:39,399
She's waiting for him,
in the garden outside.

1266
02:19:40,637 --> 02:19:43,606
I'll get her in a jiffy.

1267
02:19:44,641 --> 02:19:46,199
I' m Anju!

1268
02:19:52,249 --> 02:19:59,621
No, no, no... I' ll do
as you say from now on.

1269
02:20:00,991 --> 02:20:04,620
She's genuine!
Then come up with me quickly.

1270
02:20:05,662 --> 02:20:08,290
How can I walk?
First untie my legs.

1271
02:20:08,665 --> 02:20:12,897
They tied me up
and went away Balma!

1272
02:20:13,670 --> 02:20:18,630
- I made a mistake in judging
you. - What do you mean?

1273
02:20:20,010 --> 02:20:24,640
Meaning I didn't find
any good person in my life.

1274
02:20:25,682 --> 02:20:30,119
So I couldn't recognise
a good man with you.

1275
02:20:30,687 --> 02:20:34,958
What a sad thing! Both sisters
came together into this world...

1276
02:20:34,958 --> 02:20:38,655
...and will also leave together.

1277
02:20:39,362 --> 02:20:42,456
And with them will be
martyred this taxi driver!

1278
02:20:44,701 --> 02:20:46,259
What are you saying?

1279
02:20:50,106 --> 02:20:51,664
Doesn't matter!
I have another one.

1280
02:20:52,709 --> 02:20:57,408
You belong to me and I to you.

1281
02:21:04,721 --> 02:21:06,484
Deception! Deceit!

1282
02:21:07,724 --> 02:21:12,218
Today l' ll beat you so much that
you' ll never tease anyone again.

1283
02:21:12,329 --> 02:21:15,696
- Uncle!
- He's running away!

1284
02:21:18,735 --> 02:21:21,295
The girl got changed!
They've cheated us!

1285
02:21:21,738 --> 02:21:26,038
- Cheating Tribhuvan!
- I told you, he's a liar!

1286
02:21:26,743 --> 02:21:30,146
They' ll all die, at
my hands but dear Anju...

1287
02:21:30,146 --> 02:21:32,512
... you have to drink poison
according to the suicide note.

1288
02:21:32,749 --> 02:21:34,114
Amba, push it down her throat!

1289
02:21:35,752 --> 02:21:38,983
Jaggu! No, leave me!

1290
02:21:39,756 --> 02:21:41,189
I don't want to die!

1291
02:21:52,168 --> 02:21:55,137
Look after them!
Amba let us go.

1292
02:22:18,795 --> 02:22:21,161
Jaggu poison...

1293
02:25:30,987 --> 02:25:31,954
Sister!

1294
02:25:45,001 --> 02:25:49,700
- l' m very frightened!
- Don't be!

1295
02:25:50,006 --> 02:25:51,564
With me here
no harm will befall you.

1296
02:25:52,008 --> 02:25:58,243
- But they troubled me a lot!
- What?

1297
02:25:59,015 --> 02:26:05,477
They used to whip
me and injections...

1298
02:26:06,623 --> 02:26:10,787
-... and today...poison
- Poison?

1299
02:26:12,028 --> 02:26:14,792
- They forced me to drink
poison! - What!

1300
02:26:16,032 --> 02:26:19,798
- I don't want to die! Save me.
- Yes, sister.

1301
02:26:20,036 --> 02:26:23,802
I've found you after ages,
I won't lose you easily. Come.

1302
02:26:24,040 --> 02:26:25,598
Come. I' ll take
you to the hospital!

1303
02:26:27,043 --> 02:26:32,003
You' ll go to the
hospital if I allow you!

1304
02:26:44,060 --> 02:26:45,027
Sister!

1305
02:26:57,073 --> 02:26:59,701
Your sister is almost finished.
Soon you too will be!

1306
02:27:00,076 --> 02:27:03,307
Leave me! Sister!

1307
02:27:13,423 --> 02:27:15,391
Sister! Leave me!

1308
