- Why?

1311
02:28:29,832 --> 02:28:35,134
Because l' m a small,
little, cute, sweet baby.

1312
02:28:45,782 --> 02:28:48,444
I won't let you go. I won't!

1313
02:28:48,785 --> 02:28:49,809
How dare you!

1314
02:29:10,706 --> 02:29:13,971
You brought her just in
time. Soon she' ll be fine!

1315
02:29:39,035 --> 02:29:41,526
Tribhuvan was saved but
the law didn't spare him.

1316
02:29:43,239 --> 02:29:46,697
Jaggu took his boss's
blessings and married Anju.

1317
02:29:48,578 --> 02:29:51,376
And there Manju and
Suraj too set up a house.

1318
02:29:53,749 --> 02:29:57,742
And after exactly one year,
their children were born.

1319
02:29:58,254 --> 02:29:59,812
